$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
add_skill_level

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_skill_level -  This method adds a skill level to the specified skill to the system.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
varargs int add_skill_level(string skill,
int lvl,
mixed exp)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^skill%^RESET%^ - the skill to add a level to
%^BOLD%^lvl%^RESET%^ - the number of levels to add
%^BOLD%^exp%^RESET%^ - the amount of exp spent on the skill
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if the skill level was changed
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/skills.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a skill level to the specified skill to the
system.
.EP

